    <pre class="language-java"><code class="language-java">double te1=123456.123456;
double te2=123456.128456;
Console.log(round(te1,4));//结果:123456.1235
Console.log(round(te2,4));//结果:123456.1285</code></pre>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <code>NumberUtil.roundStr</code>&#xa0;方法主要封装<code>String.format</code>方法,舍弃方式采用四舍五入。
      </li>
    </ul>
    <pre class="language-java"><code class="language-java">double te1=123456.123456;
double te2=123456.128456;
Console.log(roundStr(te1,2));//结果:123456.12
Console.log(roundStr(te2,2));//结果:123456.13</code></pre>
  </body>
