    <p>
      我们模拟创建1000000次字符串对两者性能对比，采用<code>TimeInterval</code>计时：
    </p>
    <pre class="language-text"><code class="language-java">//StringBuilder 
TimeInterval timer = DateUtil.timer();
StringBuilder b2 = new StringBuilder();
for(int i =0; i&lt; 1000000; i++) {
&#x9;b2.append(&quot;test&quot;);
&#x9;b2 = new StringBuilder();
}
Console.log(timer.interval());</code></pre>
    <pre class="language-text"><code class="language-java">//StrBuilder
TimeInterval timer = DateUtil.timer();
StrBuilder builder = StrBuilder.create();
for(int i =0; i&lt; 1000000; i++) {
&#x9;builder.append(&quot;test&quot;);
&#x9;builder.reset();
}
Console.log(timer.interval());</code></pre>
    <p>
      测试结果为：
    </p>
    <pre class="language-text"><code class="language-java">StringBuilder: 39ms
StrBuilder   : 20ms</code></pre>
    <p>
      性能几乎翻倍。也欢迎用户自行测试。
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
