  <body>
    <p>
      Hutool针对<code>java.security.Signature</code>做了简化包装，包装类为：<code>Sign</code>，用于生成签名和签名验证。
    </p>
    <p>
      对于签名算法，Hutool封装了JDK的Signature，具体介绍见：<a href="https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/technotes/guides/security/StandardNames.html#Signature" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/technotes/guides/security/StandardNames.html#Signature&#xa0; <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" x="0px" y="0px" viewbox="0 0 100 100" width="15" height="15" class="icon outbound">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;<path fill="currentColor" d="M18.8,85.1h56l0,0c2.2,0,4-1.8,4-4v-32h-8v28h-48v-48h28v-8h-32l0,0c-2.2,0-4,1.8-4,4v56C14.8,83.3,16.6,85.1,18.8,85.1z"></path>&#xa0;<polygon fill="currentColor" points="45.7,48.7 51.3,54.3 77.2,28.5 77.2,37.2 85.2,37.2 85.2,14.9 62.8,14.9 62.8,22.9 71.5,22.9"></polygon>&#xa0; </svg>&#xa0;<span class="sr-only">(opens new window)</span></a>：
    </p>
    <pre class="language-java"><code class="language-java">// The RSA signature algorithm
NONEwithRSA
// The MD2/MD5 with RSA Encryption signature algorithm
