  <body>
    <p>
      Hutool默认提供了简单的文件服务，即定义一个root目录，则请求路径后直接访问目录下的资源，默认请求<code>index.html</code>，类似于Nginx。
    </p>
    <pre class="language-text"><code class="language-java">HttpUtil.createServer(8888)
    // 设置默认根目录
    .setRoot(&quot;D:\\workspace\\site\\hutool-site&quot;)
    .start();</code></pre>
    <p>
      此时访问<a href="http://localhost:8888/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">http://localhost:8888/&#xa0; <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" x="0px" y="0px" viewbox="0 0 100 100" width="15" height="15" class="icon outbound">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;<path fill="currentColor" d="M18.8,85.1h56l0,0c2.2,0,4-1.8,4-4v-32h-8v28h-48v-48h28v-8h-32l0,0c-2.2,0-4,1.8-4,4v56C14.8,83.3,16.6,85.1,18.8,85.1z"></path>&#xa0;<polygon fill="currentColor" points="45.7,48.7 51.3,54.3 77.2,28.5 77.2,37.2 85.2,37.2 85.2,14.9 62.8,14.9 62.8,22.9 71.5,22.9"></polygon>&#xa0; </svg>&#xa0;<span class="sr-only">(opens new window)</span></a>即可访问HTML静态页面。
    </p>
    <blockquote>
      <p>
        hutool-site是Hutool主页的源码项目，地址在：<a href="https://gitee.com/loolly_admin/hutool-site" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://gitee.com/loolly_admin/hutool-site&#xa0; <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" x="0px" y="0px" viewbox="0 0 100 100" width="15" height="15" class="icon outbound">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;<path fill="currentColor" d="M18.8,85.1h56l0,0c2.2,0,4-1.8,4-4v-32h-8v28h-48v-48h28v-8h-32l0,0c-2.2,0-4,1.8-4,4v56C14.8,83.3,16.6,85.1,18.8,85.1z"></path>&#xa0;<polygon fill="currentColor" points="45.7,48.7 51.3,54.3 77.2,28.5 77.2,37.2 85.2,37.2 85.2,14.9 62.8,14.9 62.8,22.9 71.5,22.9"></polygon>&#xa0; </svg>&#xa0;<span class="sr-only">(opens new window)</span></a>，下载后配合SimpleServer实现离线文档。
      </p>
