    </p>
    <p>
      Hutool针对常见中文分词库做了统一接口封装，即定义一套规范，隔离各个库的差异，做到一段代码，随意更换。
    </p>
    <p>
      Hutool现在封装的引擎有：
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <a href="https://github.com/NLPchina/ansj_seg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ansj&#xa0; <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" x="0px" y="0px" viewbox="0 0 100 100" width="15" height="15" class="icon outbound">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;<path fill="currentColor" d="M18.8,85.1h56l0,0c2.2,0,4-1.8,4-4v-32h-8v28h-48v-48h28v-8h-32l0,0c-2.2,0-4,1.8-4,4v56C14.8,83.3,16.6,85.1,18.8,85.1z"></path>&#xa0;<polygon fill="currentColor" points="45.7,48.7 51.3,54.3 77.2,28.5 77.2,37.2 85.2,37.2 85.2,14.9 62.8,14.9 62.8,22.9 71.5,22.9"></polygon>&#xa0; </svg>&#xa0;<span class="sr-only">(opens new window)</span></a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://github.com/hankcs/HanLP" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">HanLP&#xa0; <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" x="0px" y="0px" viewbox="0 0 100 100" width="15" height="15" class="icon outbound">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;<path fill="currentColor" d="M18.8,85.1h56l0,0c2.2,0,4-1.8,4-4v-32h-8v28h-48v-48h28v-8h-32l0,0c-2.2,0-4,1.8-4,4v56C14.8,83.3,16.6,85.1,18.8,85.1z"></path>&#xa0;<polygon fill="currentColor" points="45.7,48.7 51.3,54.3 77.2,28.5 77.2,37.2 85.2,37.2 85.2,14.9 62.8,14.9 62.8,22.9 71.5,22.9"></polygon>&#xa0; </svg>&#xa0;<span class="sr-only">(opens new window)</span></a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://github.com/yozhao/IKAnalyzer" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">IKAnalyzer&#xa0; <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" x="0px" y="0px" viewbox="0 0 100 100" width="15" height="15" class="icon outbound">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;<path fill="currentColor" d="M18.8,85.1h56l0,0c2.2,0,4-1.8,4-4v-32h-8v28h-48v-48h28v-8h-32l0,0c-2.2,0-4,1.8-4,4v56C14.8,83.3,16.6,85.1,18.8,85.1z"></path>&#xa0;<polygon fill="currentColor" points="45.7,48.7 51.3,54.3 77.2,28.5 77.2,37.2 85.2,37.2 85.2,14.9 62.8,14.9 62.8,22.9 71.5,22.9"></polygon>&#xa0; </svg>&#xa0;<span class="sr-only">(opens new window)</span></a>
