<node ID="ID_1401528042" CREATED="1754457029352" MODIFIED="1754464472824"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    介绍
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      与模板引擎类似，Hutool针对较为流行的表达式计算引擎封装为门面模式，提供统一的API，去除差异。 现有的引擎实现有：
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <a href="https://github.com/killme2008/aviatorscript" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Aviator&#xa0; <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" x="0px" y="0px" viewbox="0 0 100 100" width="15" height="15" class="icon outbound">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;<path fill="currentColor" d="M18.8,85.1h56l0,0c2.2,0,4-1.8,4-4v-32h-8v28h-48v-48h28v-8h-32l0,0c-2.2,0-4,1.8-4,4v56C14.8,83.3,16.6,85.1,18.8,85.1z"></path>&#xa0;<polygon fill="currentColor" points="45.7,48.7 51.3,54.3 77.2,28.5 77.2,37.2 85.2,37.2 85.2,14.9 62.8,14.9 62.8,22.9 71.5,22.9"></polygon>&#xa0; </svg>&#xa0;<span class="sr-only">(opens new window)</span></a>
